E[X] = \sum_{i=0}^{n-1} i \cdot P(\text{i failures followed by success})
=\sum_{i=1}^{n-1} i \cdot \underbrace{ \frac{n-1}{n}\cdot  \frac{n-2}{n-1}\cdots   \frac{n-i+1}{n-i+2}\cdot \frac{n-i}{n-i+1}}_{i \text{ failed trials}}\cdot \underbrace{\frac{1}{n-i}}_{success}
=\sum_{i=1}^{n-1} i \cdot \frac{1}{n} 
=\frac{1}{n}(n-1)\frac{1+(n-1)}{2}
= \frac{n-1}{2}
